reviewText: Some disc in series 300 seem to lock up my dvd player.  I contacted Ms. Payne and she sent me replacements immediately. They replacements work great and I am very happy.  Will order from her again.

I purchased for my Granddaughter who expressed an interest in acrylic art.  After a little research I purchased this video.  It is perfect, provided techinic that was easy to understand and follow.  Granddaughter is learning quickly and references the video often.
